cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with adversarial training of neural networks. It could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as adversarial training is commonly used in image classification tasks. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as adversarial training is a popular method in the field of AI. It may also be classified under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural networks. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as adversarial training is used to improve the security of machine learning models against attacks.
